<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṭaiyār tiruvaikā vuṭaiyārkku Irā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi> vaḷanāṭṭup paravaiccuṟṟu pūṇṭi Uṭaiyāṉ tillai nāyakaṉ kaṇavati nampiyāṉa maturānta
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ka vaṉṉāṭuṭaiyāṉ Ikkōyil tāṉattārku Upaiyaṅkuṭutta paricāvatu Ivaṉ pitākkoṇṭu ṭaiyarāy Ivar Apāpattil <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
